RATVOLUTION.readme

Ratvolution is the videgame created as a final project of the Master en Creación y Diseño de Videojuegos at Universitat Politècnica de Catalunya during 2014-2015 course.
It's a multicharacter puzzle/tactics game in real time that features a really cool visual style and enables for multiple resolutions for the same situation, having to master the combination of the abilities and items from the three characters to complete each phase.
The game has a tutorial level, one full complete level and a "boss" stage.
To download and try the game, please download all the "Ejecutable" zipped parts and unzip them in your folder of choice. Then run the Ratvolution.exe.
